# BigData University Quality - Project Objectives

## Project Overview
This project aims to analyze and improve university quality through big data analytics.

## Main Objectives
1. **Data Collection**: Gather comprehensive university quality metrics
2. **Analysis**: Apply big data techniques to identify quality patterns
3. **Visualization**: Create meaningful dashboards and reports
4. **Recommendations**: Provide actionable insights for university improvement

## Success Criteria
- [ ] Complete data collection from multiple sources
- [ ] Implement robust data processing pipeline
- [ ] Deliver comprehensive quality analysis
- [ ] Present findings in accessible format

## Timeline
- Planning Phase: Week 1-2
- Data Collection: Week 3-5
- Analysis Phase: Week 6-10
- Report Writing: Week 11-12

## Resources Required
- Data sources and APIs
- Computing resources for big data processing
- Visualization tools
- Academic literature and references
